business_details.Business: P/A issued against accused Smt. Basanti Munda returned with report that that the accused is not traceable. Nobody could say anything about her present location.          Also the Proclamation is duly served and hang in conspicious place. More over no any moveable and immoveable properties belonging in her name could be found.       Seen the P/A report of the E.O. I find it satisfactory that the P/A has been executed properly by the E.O. Therefore examination of E.O is hereby dispensed with. The accused Smt. Basanti Munda is declared absconder and the case against her is filed till her arrest.              The case is disposed off.
